640741]飚车小能手[/uid] (2026-06-16 11:08):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，五月的工业增加值小超预期，投资和消费不及预期，你之前四月时关于六月国内双降的看法有变化吗[s:ac:愁][/quote]<br/>我们的策略是应对式的  不以我们自己的数据为主 目前还没有到不放水就会死的状态", "lou": 3241, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 871887018, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781579438}, {"pid": 871890671, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 93, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 11:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "踏空的资金还是太多了 而且还很怕<br/>是不是前面下跌通道被打怕了？<br/>所以你们知道没 没实力要么不做下跌通道 保证自己的盈利，要么踩准节奏，左右横跳<br/>不然现在心态炸了 要恢复起来没那么容易<br/><br/>现在外面的资金太小心了 就是那种 又怕死又反动 <br/>明牌想给他们点甜头他们都不敢进来的资金。", "lou": 3242, "content_length": 250, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781580794}, {"pid": 871890800, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 40, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 11:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871890294,45974302,7381]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65664557]维拉帕米不是米[/uid] (2026-06-16 11:30):[/b]<br/><br/>黄金跟黄金股是两回事，并且，黄金算有色股，你自己看看狼大说了啥[/quote]<br/>黄金算贵金属 不算有色股<br/>不过我是不会去黄金股的  没必要", "lou": 3243, "content_length": 55, "reply_to": 871890294, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781580849}, {"pid": 871891696, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 52, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 11:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871891493,45974302,7382]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=6313142]暮残[/uid] (2026-06-16 11:38):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大狼大，铜股那边有什么搞头么，还是最近的趋势只当超跌反弹看<br/>铜期货都快摸新高了，铜股也是腰斩最近底部才刚放量2根大阳线。<br/>买铜股一定意义上也是觉得，铜作为工业金属，一方面跟电相关，一方面也跟AIDC建设相关<br/>虽然说弃铜用光，但是机柜外还是需要铜的吧[/quote]<br/>嗯  目前判断工业金属里最优解", "lou": 3244, "content_length": 31, "reply_to": 871891493, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781581211}, {"pid": 871891869, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 47, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 11:41", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871891659,45974302,7382]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42633665]Hugvn_1[/uid] (2026-06-16 11:39):[/b]<br/><br/>？不是小日子加息一根冲天直线是什么意思？是我认知出现问题了吗？这是利好吗？[s:ac:咦][/quote]<br/>我前面分析过了 是利空落地 这件事情属于符合预期的利好", "lou": 3245, "content_length": 55, "reply_to": 871891659, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781581285}, {"pid": 871892488, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 70, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 11:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871892352,45974302,7383]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42488939]rosylips[/uid] (2026-06-16 11:45):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大怎么看待材料设备这块发散到极致的概念细分？<br/>昨天研究了一下，包括之前的钨和钼，铜，已经不算严格的有色金属或者稀土概念了，多少带有一点科技色彩，pcb啊，半导体，芯片，目前从硅片开始轮动的行情也已经蔓延到无机非金属材料上去了，之前的蚀刻，显影，气体等，这样的行情还是延续之前的不断缩圈细分为止？还是说会伴随不断稀缺的产品衍生出来的材料稀缺，在后期的放量同步放大？[/quote]<br/>现在都是吹票行情 不要讨论基本面<br/>谁的小作文多谁能涨<br/>具体的我之前分析过了<br/>现在你才跟我谈半导体材料基本面 晚了", "lou": 3246, "content_length": 107, "reply_to": 871892352, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781581579}, {"pid": 871892787, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 11:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871892626,45974302,7383]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67024871]焦糖奶昔[/uid] (2026-06-16 11:47):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:汗]别的不知道 铜应该不用科技来抬 股票不涨是另一回事[/quote]<br/>我叫SORA和你说我对铜的判断。", "lou": 3247, "content_length": 33, "reply_to": 871892626, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781581703}, {"pid": 871893836, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 48, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 11:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871893486,45974302,7384]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61422464]kaiserDu[/uid] (2026-06-16 11:54):[/b]<br/><br/>这不牛市旗手来打样了么~目前看效果一般[/quote]<br/>兜底券商的资金是做科技的机构 <br/>你没想到吧", "lou": 3248, "content_length": 43, "reply_to": 871893486, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781582227}, {"pid": 871895015, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 12:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871894739,45974302,7384]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62862742]織田信姬[/uid] (2026-06-16 12:04):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 请问一下 现在指数缩量涨 而且没有之前科技吸血的现象 是不是机构故意的 为了把空仓的人骗进来再来一波科技吸血老登放血的场面啊[s:ac:茶][/quote]<br/>昨天说过了 跟故意没关系", "lou": 3249, "content_length": 27, "reply_to": 871894739, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781582835}, {"pid": 871898004, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 102, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 12:35", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871897078,45974302,7386]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1007252]ghjt[/uid] (2026-06-16 12:26):[/b]<br/><br/>那这种情况下对于踏空资金来说，是不是还是越早杀进来越好<br/>虽然很怕自己买在山顶，但是如果最终还是会忍不住进来，那么越早进越可能被后面进来的人抬轿子[/quote]<br/>现在杀进来吃到肉不难<br/>难的是中间如何稳住和最后能不能不贪把盈利带走<br/>在股市里 起点不是很重要 重要的是终点", "lou": 3250, "content_length": 103, "reply_to": 871897078, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781584507}, {"pid": 871901221, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 13:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871900828,45974302,7389]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41544856]闻空言语[/uid] (2026-06-16 13:03):[/b]<br/><br/>踏空资金一直不敢进，那就涨到他们忍不住？[/quote]<br/>差不多了  缩转放的时候他们就进来了", "lou": 3251, "content_length": 37, "reply_to": 871900828, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781586461}, {"pid": 871902831, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 28, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 13:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871901806,45974302,7389]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=295108]jimddr[/uid] (2026-06-16 13:13):[/b]<br/><br/>观测到开始微微放量<br/><br/>狼大狼大，AI软这一波会跟上吗？<br/>电力投错了，没选西电错失大肉，感觉AI软可能到底部了，想要转投软件方向了[s:ac:冷][/quote]<br/>AI软?港股质朴", "lou": 3252, "content_length": 18, "reply_to": 871901806, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781587399}, {"pid": 871904385, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 138, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 13:38", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "事到如今 <br/>我最对不起的就是铜箔[s:ac:冷]", "lou": 3253, "content_length": 26, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781588306}, {"pid": 871905023, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 30, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 13:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871904758,45974302,7394]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67169221]开一局_[/uid] (2026-06-16 13:42):[/b]<br/><br/>好哥哥们收了神通吧，别再空核心科技了，空一下题材啊[s:ac:喘][/quote]<br/>科创50跌的还没银行保险多。。。。。", "lou": 3254, "content_length": 39, "reply_to": 871904758, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781588677}, {"pid": 871905630, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 81, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 13:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871905321,45974302,7396]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60646519]andylaw123[/uid] (2026-06-16 13:47):[/b]<br/><br/>完了， 昨天让我妈卖中一，晚上要挨骂了[s:ac:哭1][/quote]<br/>家庭地位-1<br/>可能低于宠物", "lou": 3255, "content_length": 27, "reply_to": 871905321, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781588994}, {"pid": 871906351, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 59, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 13:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871906130,45974302,7398]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60062729]北府小卒[/uid] (2026-06-16 13:54):[/b]<br/><br/>楼里大佬多我想问下使劲砸红利真的有用吗[/quote]<br/>还是不是散户自己卖的  机构都没持仓了<br/>就是忘了自己只吃利息的初心  看见自己的还在跌 科技不跌 自己就忍不住出去了", "lou": 3256, "content_length": 107, "reply_to": 871906130, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781589412}, {"pid": 871906674, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 77, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 13:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871906591,45974302,7398]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42719239]我呆毛王天下第一[/uid] (2026-06-16 13:59):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大那是不是逆练心法，相当于红利目前已经是情绪超跌的状态，后续如果切换可以考虑抄一下呢[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>我实在不懂  在牛市里面吃股息是什么逻辑<br/>我没有这个逻辑", "lou": 3257, "content_length": 55, "reply_to": 871906591, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781589593}, {"pid": 871907493, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 14:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871907198,45974302,7400]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42719239]我呆毛王天下第一[/uid] (2026-06-16 14:04):[/b]<br/><br/>啊，想着是四浪的时候科技出来的资金会到一些超跌的低风险板块去[s:ac:怕]原来不是嘛[/quote]<br/>4浪我不激进 万一4浪转下跌一浪呢 <br/>他和前段时间那种ABC杀不一样  预期不一样<br/>所以我宁可不做", "lou": 3258, "content_length": 86, "reply_to": 871907198, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781590023}, {"pid": 871909449, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 59, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-16 14:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871908930,45974302,7403]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67152878]贤希圣[/uid] (2026-06-16 14:18):[/b]<br/><br/>说到四浪，狼哥正好请教一下，如果核心科技的业绩中报时间跟下跌浪叠在一起了，是要撑着还是顺势而为先撤再说呢？[/quote]<br/>业绩披露完不都是要跌的么 因为机构会重新按照披露的业绩调仓换股<br/>我倒是希望这个时间别叠加本身的技术4浪  到时候会很麻烦。速度有可能会很快。", "lou": 3259, "content_length": 136, "reply_to": 871908930, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781590982}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155636, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782111206, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "6497646d", "digest": 0, "last